    "ministry_url": "https://curriculum.gov.bc.ca/curriculum/adst/12/metalwork",
    "description": "Students develop advanced metal fabrication skills including structural steel work, welding, forming, and finishing. This course emphasizes professional metalworking techniques, safety practices, and industry applications.",
    "general_description": "Advanced metal fabrication, structural steel, welding, and industry applications.",
